Template for STM32F4 Development on the Ubuntu mate 15.04.
The main.c file contains a basic example showing the bluetooth module HC-06.
Following steps is below
	build:
		make

	clean: 
		make clean

	run:
		make flash

P.S. To maintain your coding style. You can try this! Make sure that you have installed astyle.
$ astyle --style=kr --indent=spaces=4 --indent-switches --suffix=none *.[ch]
